article.story: NASHVILLE, Tenn. -- — Jacob Ognacevic's 20 points helped Lipscomb defeat Southeast Missouri State 78-60 on Thursday. Ognacevic added seven rebounds for the Bisons (6-4). Gyasi Powell scored 19 points, going 6 of 9 (5 for 8 from 3-point range). Dylan Faulkner shot 5 of 8 from the field and 3 for 6 from the line to finish with 13 points, while adding nine rebounds. Troy Cole Jr. finished with 10 points and six rebounds for the Redhawks (3-5). ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
